Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:53.31,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(568,551)}人生游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:55.03,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\3c&HC6593E&\pos(552,502)}赌上的东西…
